263
00:27:31,590 --> 00:27:35,510
This medicine is not easy to make. The ingredients are rare and they come for a high price.

264
00:27:35,510 --> 00:27:37,800
The brewing method is especially bothersome.

265
00:27:37,800 --> 00:27:39,550
