282
00:29:12,840 --> 00:29:16,030
This morning I called you, you wouldn't get up. You even said if I kept nagging, you'd beat me to a pulp.

283
00:29:16,030 --> 00:29:17,930
Even if the sky fell down, it wouldn't have disturbed your sleep.

284
00:29:17,930 --> 00:29:20,490
I want to beat you to a pulp right now!

285
00:29:28,450 --> 00:29:31,720
You want to run? Dream on!

286
00:29:31,720 --> 00:29:36,390
